{"prompt": "Generate a website for a local artist portfolio. The website should be rustic and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Rustic Artistry</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --primary-color: #4a6d85;\n            --secondary-color: #a3b9c8;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #f5f0e1;\n            --accent-color: #7a90a1;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Georgia', serif;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            font-size: 3em;\n            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 2rem auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n        }\n\n        section {\n            margin-bottom: 2rem;\n            padding: 1.5rem;\n            background-color: #ffffff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        h2 {\n            color: var(--primary-color);\n            border-bottom: 2px solid var(--accent-color);\n            padding-bottom: 0.5rem;\n            margin-bottom: 1rem;\n        }\n\n        .gallery {\n            display: grid;\n            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n            gap: 1.5rem;\n        }\n\n        .artwork {\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            border: 1px solid var(--secondary-color);\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            padding: 1rem;\n            text-align: center;\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .artwork:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-5px);\n            box-shadow: 0 6px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);\n        }\n\n        .artwork img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            margin-bottom: 0.8rem;\n            border: 2px solid var(--primary-color);\n        }\n\n        .artwork h3 {\n            margin-top: 0;\n            color: var(--accent-color);\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n        }\n\n        .artwork p {\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            color: #555;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--primary-color);\n            color: white;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 2rem 0;\n            margin-top: 2rem;\n            border-top: 5px solid var(--accent-color);\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a {\n            color: white;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            font-weight: bold;\n        }\n\n        .contact-info a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header>\n        <h1>Whispering Pines Studio</h1>\n        <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; color: var(--secondary-color);\">Art by Elias Thorne</p>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <section id=\"about\">\n            <h2>About the Artist</h2>\n            <p>Welcome to my humble studio, nestled amongst the whispering pines. Here, I capture the essence of nature's quiet beauty through oil and watercolor. Each piece is an invitation to pause, reflect, and reconnect with the world around us.</p>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"gallery\">\n            <h2>Art Gallery</h2>\n            <div class=\"gallery\">\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a6d85/ffffff?text=Forest+Path\" alt=\"Forest Path Painting\">\n                    <h3>Forest Path</h3>\n                    <p>An oil painting capturing the tranquility of a sun-dappled forest trail.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/7a90a1/ffffff?text=Mountain+Lake\" alt=\"Mountain Lake Watercolor\">\n                    <h3>Mountain Lake</h3>\n                    <p>A watercolor depicting the serene reflections of a crisp mountain lake.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/4a6d85/ffffff?text=Autumn+Hues\" alt=\"Autumn Hues Canvas\">\n                    <h3>Autumn Hues</h3>\n                    <p>Vibrant strokes of oil on canvas, showcasing the rich colors of fall.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"artwork\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/a3b9c8/ffffff?text=Seaside+Breeze\" alt=\"Seaside Breeze Sketch\">\n                    <h3>Seaside Breeze</h3>\n                    <p>A delicate charcoal sketch inspired by the coastal air.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <section id=\"contact\">\n            <h2>Contact</h2>\n            <div class=\"contact-info\">\n                <p>For inquiries, commissions, or to simply say hello, please reach out:</p>\n                <p>Email: <a href=\"mailto:elias.thorne.art@email.com\">elias.thorne.art@email.com</a></p>\n                <p>Instagram: <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\">@WhisperingPinesArt</a></p>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <p>&copy; 2023 Whispering Pines Studio. All rights reserved.</p>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple animation on scroll for gallery items\n        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {\n            const galleryItems = document.querySelectorAll('.artwork');\n\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = '1';\n                        entry.target.style.transform = 'scale(1.05)';\n                        galleryItems.forEach(item => {\n                            if (item !== entry.target) {\n                                item.style.opacity = '0.7';\n                                item.style.transform = 'scale(1)';\n                            }\n                        });\n                    } else {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = '0.7';\n                        entry.target.style.transform = 'scale(1)';\n                    }\n                });\n            }, {\n                threshold: 0.2\n            });\n\n            galleryItems.forEach(item => {\n                item.style.opacity = '0.7'; // Initial state for fade-in\n                item.style.transform = 'scale(1)'; // Initial state for scale-up\n                observer.observe(item);\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}